c: 5
v: 19
t: "O Population of the Book, (Or: Family of the Book, i.e., the Jews and Christians) Our Messenger has already come to you making (things) evident to you, upon an interval between the Messengers, that you should not say, \"In no way has there come to us any bearer of good tidings, nor a warner.\" Yet (now) there has already come to you a bearer of good tidings and a warner; and Allah is Ever-Determiner over everything"